modName: Lyra the Beautiful Nord_still in helgen
summary: A save file of Lyra. She is a nord. She is waiting at he choping block of helgen.
descriptionHtml:
This is lyra. She is a nord and her position in game is right before she is called to the choping block. Don\'t be confused by the screenshots ;)

If you want her to look like the screenshots you will need:
(none of these mods were made by me)

Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

Covereyes by mrLenski:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4869
(any one)
Coverwomen by mrLenski:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563
(download No 3)

ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168

After a request there is also Lyra with a Vanilla hair style!

Once you open the save file, if a pop-up tells you that there is missing content (or something similar) don\'t worry. It is just that you don\'t have all the weapon and armour mods I have.
author: DarkMonster
